{
  "stem": "11144.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Then, we were-- after-- after living in this-- in those huts or whatever-- hut, really, not chalet-- we would go to-- we would, again, have to move.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Because somebody would say that Germans are close by.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So we would move.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And my mother would, again, develop some relation with some Poles.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And they would let us stay on the-- over the-- over a barn, in-- you know, in straw upstairs.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So we would be laying there the whole day, not be able to move.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Because--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And my sister.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, just me and my mother and my sister.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I don't remember if my uncle was-- whether he was with us or not at that time.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we were hiding there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And at night, they would bring us some food.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And when we had to go to the bathroom, it was going at night.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We had to hold the whole day.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We couldn't-- couldn't walk down from there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And again, we heard people coming, and neighbors, and whatever.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And everybody was snooping because whatever.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Then, again, when we were traveling from one village to another, from one place of the forest to another, we would end up in somebody's field and sleep in a hay-- in a big hay--",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--haystack.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, my mother would go in and just make-- like, pull out something.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the hay is very warm.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So we could survive.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And in the middle of the night, we would hear dogs barking.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we would hear somebody would say, oh my god.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "What's happening now?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Why that the dog is barking now?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Well, maybe the Germans are around the corner-- and you know, things like that.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, but it would have been, again.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But these forests were quite thick.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the forests were quite big.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
